reviewText: I bought this movie not because of the actors or story line, those are solid "B" movie ingredients.  I bought it because it was filmed in historic parts of El-Jobean, Florida and wanted to see how it related to the movie.
Finally a movie with some substance and not just entertainment. Encourages one to consider what is really important in life. Enjoyed it very much.
I enjoyed watching this movie it was very interesting and rewarding makes one examine their own motives. I would probably in the future order it as a gift for someone else.
